# BEAD Issue Directories
#
# Issues are organized by assigned agent:
# - inbox/     - New issues awaiting assignment
# - coder/     - Component Coder tasks
# - tester/    - Test Writer tasks
# - reviewer/  - Code Reviewer tasks
# - dispatcher/ - Dispatcher Config tasks
# - docs/      - Documentation Agent tasks
# - blocked/   - Issues waiting on external input
# - completed/ - Archived completed issues
